# ⚠️ CURRENT PARALLEL TRACK: INTRO INTAKE RUNTIME (AI INTEGRATION)

STATUS: IN PROGRESS (MAJOR PROGRESS MADE)

RATIONALE:
We intentionally moved ahead of orchestration layers (XState / Temporal)
to unlock learning and motivation through real AI interaction.

This is a VALID deviation because:
- it increases learning velocity
- it grounds abstract architecture in real systems
- it validates contracts against real model behavior

