# INTRO INTAKE — CURRENT SYSTEM STATE

You now have a fully working pipeline:

```
CLI message
→ AI (OpenAI)
→ extractText (normalize)
→ JSON.parse
→ Zod validation (IntroExtractionSchema)
→ map → rawProposal
→ ingestion pipeline (intakeStage)
```

